map u scroll half-up
map d scroll half-down
map <S-Space> navigate previous
map <Space>   navigate next

map r reload
map R rotate
map = zoom in
map - zoom out

# Page fit
map D toggle_page_mode
map f adjust_window best-fit
map F adjust_window width

